					<msContents class="#CM">
						<summary><p>Bound codex, made of folios and quires of various measurements. Contains copies, commissioned by Édouard Ariel (as attested by his autograph colophons), of official documents pertaining to Pondicherry. Bears the title <title xml:lang="ta">Putuccēri Tiṉacaritai Aṉupantam</title> on the spine.</p>
<p>See also BnF Indien 143.</p>
<p>A composite manuscript treated here as a multi-text manuscript for convenience.</p>
<p>Segmentation in units (U1) to be revised and updated.</p></summary>

						
